			<string>PSGroupCell</string>
			<key>footerText</key>
			<string>Each app has custom notification settings that determine where their notifications are allowed to show (in Settings â€”> Notifications). This menu allows you to restrict Pusher to only send a notification if the app's notification settings have either all (AND) or at least one (OR) of the selected options below. Selecting AND requires all of the enabled options below to be enabled in the app's settings. Selecting OR requires only one of the enabled options below to be enabled in the app's settings.</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>cell</key>
			<string>PSSegmentCell</string>
			<key>default</key>
			<true/>
			<key>defaults</key>
			<string>com.noahsaso.pusher</string>
			<key>PostNotification</key>
			<string>com.noahsaso.pusher/prefs</string>
			<key>detail</key>
			<string>PSListItemsController</string>
			<key>key</key>
			<string>SufficientNotificationSettingsIsAnd</string>
			<key>validTitles</key>
