				<string>AND</string>
				<string>OR</string>
			</array>
			<key>validValues</key>
			<array>
				<true/>
				<false/>
			</array>
		</dict>

		<dict>
			<key>cell</key>
			<string>PSGroupCell</string>
			<key>footerText</key>
			<string>When using OR, you will probably want to require that Allow Notifications is enabled in the app's notification settings in addition to other settings. This is because the device saves the rest of the settings (e.g. Lock Screen, Badges, etc.) even when you turn off Allow Notifications in the app's notification settings. For example, if you install a new app and don't allow push notifications, the rest of the settings still default to on. If you select OR, Lock Screen, and Sounds below for example, even the apps that hide all notifications will be sent through Pusher. This fixes that. When this option is on, you will probably want to disable the 'Allow Notifications' switch below. If you are confused, leave this setting on.</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
